<seg id=140> Lanzhou Price Bureau Gives Explanation of Price Controls on Beef Noodles: It's Only Because the Rises have been Too Large</seg>
<seg id=141> Chinanews.com, Lanzhou, July 10 (Huang Dang)</seg>
<seg id=142> This afternoon, the Lanzhou municipal price bureau invited the departments concerned and held a seminar on the price controls on beef noodles.</seg>
