<seg id=608> (International) Spain: Masked Husband Arrested after Trying to Kill Wife</seg>
<seg id=609> MADRID, July 7 (Xinhua) A woman in Spain attacked by a masked robber was astonished to discover the attacker was actually her husband when she pulled the mask off the robber in the struggle. Police has arrested him.</seg>
<seg id=610> According media reports here on the 6th, the woman worked at a bakery in the city of Valencia.</seg>
<seg id=611> One day, a masked man burst into the shop. She thought it was a robber and so told him to take money from the till and leave.</seg>
