<seg id=669> Presently, seven containers of White Rabbit creamy candy were being shipped to countries including Singapore, Costa Rica, Malaysia, India, Nepal and the United States.</seg>
<seg id=670> (International) Criminal Suspect Arrested for Making British Supermarket Bomb Threats</seg>
